Package neureka.common.utility

Class Cache<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • neureka.common.utility.Cache<O>
  • Type Parameters:
    O - The type that should be cached, this may be an NDConfiguration or int[] array.
    public final class Cache<O>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a simple, fixed size cache for immutable objects which are shared throughout the library runtime... This is an internal class which should not be used outside of Neurekas internals.
